title: Looking for silver ADC duo
body: SoloQ ADCs always suck. Looking for someone who isn't an ape to duo with.

replies.body: Always happy to duo but lets do one norm first to make sure that synergy is there.
Ik how you feel man, I am a good adc, sliver 3, name:Kusuo, I usually play in the afternoon or morning because that's  when I'm not lagging. We warmup in a Norma then we start to duo :)
